data.description: Enjoy Life near area parks, trails, and lakes -- enjoy a neighborhood park just across the street! Gorgeous 2018-built 4-bedroom home, convenient to shopping, recreational opportunities, and easy commutes to work! This wonderful Home has so much to offer and is ready for new Owners! 4 spacious bedrooms, 3 full baths, great Island Kitchen open to comfortable Living-Den with gas-log Fireplace and view of the backyard. Primary Bedroom with ensuite Bath, Guest or 4th Bedroom privately located downstairs. 2 Bedrooms, Full Bath as well as Huge Gameroom and fabulous Media Room are on 2nd level. HUGE PLUS - Media Room includes 125-inch Movie Screen, 4K BenQ Film Projector, Onkyo 7.1.2 Sound System, Klipsch Speakers, sound-proofing wall panels, and 3 plush black leather Media Seats! Impressive Wood Flooring, soaring ceilings in the main living, tons of storage and bedroom closet space, and remaining builder warranty, all add up to a fantastic place to live! Come see this Home quickly!
